com.ibm.wala.util.intset

Class BitSet<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wala.util.intset.BitSet<T>

  • public final class BitSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A bit set is a set of elements, each of which corresponds to a unique integer from [0,MAX].
